        <section class="hipcamp" id="camp">
            <div class="container hipcamp-content">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Hipcamp launch coming soon</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">Primitive stays are open now via email. Hipcamp reservations will open once post-Helene rebuilds wrap and reviews can follow.</p>
                    <a class="button" href="camp.html">Campsite overview</a>
                </div>
                <article class="hipcamp-card">
                    <h3>What to expect</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Primitive tent area with fire pit and pasture views.</li>
                        <li>RVs allowed; hookups available only at the hangar.</li>
                        <li>Hangar lounge with bathroom access and workspace.</li>
                        <li>Quiet mornings with Blue Ridge foothill fog.</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="developer-showcase" id="apps">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Build log</h2>
