                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <article class="feature-card">
                        <h3>GitHub activity</h3>
                        <p>Latest commits, repos, and contributions from the Flying Changes Farm workshop.</p>
                        <iframe class="github-feed" src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api?username=StoneHub&show_icons=true&hide_rank=true&include_all_commits=true&bg_color=ffffff00" title="GitHub activity for StoneHub" loading="lazy"></iframe>
                    </article>
                    <article class="feature-card">
                        <h3 id="pickmyroute">PickMyRoute</h3>
                        <p>Route visualization tool for coordinating supply runs between the farm, hangar, and launch sites.</p>
                        <a href="https://github.com/StoneHub" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Follow progress →</a>
                    </article>
                    <article class="feature-card">
                        <h3 id="care-calendar">Care Calendar</h3>
                        <p>Caregiver scheduling app balancing household needs with farm chores and recovery work.</p>
                        <a href="https://github.com/StoneHub" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">View repository →</a>
                    </article>
                    <article class="feature-card">
                        <h3 id="legacy">Legacy projects</h3>
